Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望能收到禮物！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:44.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:47.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖誕老人一定會給你禮物的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂最好也來許個願吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:58.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望今年能是一個白色聖誕節
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.93,0:01:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色聖誕節？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.06,0:01:05.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是雪花飄飄  遍地銀白的聖誕節
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.48,0:01:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂  憂！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.28,0:01:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.99,0:01:21.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鏘鏘～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色聖誕節哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.58,0:01:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.93,0:01:52.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.21,0:01:55.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐墊裡的棉花
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.08,0:01:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.98,0:02:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是那天  姐姐被訓了很長時間
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂  在笑什麼呢
